title: Online Dating Real Time Assist (Episode 215)
description:
Show Notes: 

04:15 - The best message for creating intrigue and how to respond to her typical response.

10:00 - Why a client who quit online dating is considering coming back to it.

11:30 - How to troubleshoot when you lose a girl mid role play script.

14:25 - How to revive a dead conversation.

16:42 - What makes a good and bad online dating profile prompt.

18:18 - Three perfect prompts to set a sexual tone and position yourself correctly on the dating apps.

21:30 - What do you say to this... "I'm looking for a sex slave to worship me and get rewarded."

24:16 - If you go sexual online, are you taking too big of a risk or positioning yourself poorly?

25:26 - When she doesn't respond for a week.

27:28 - Why double texting was the correct move and the right time.

31:38 - Why you need scripts to train and how to ween yourself off them.
